!begin_node Scrap library
!html_name scrp

This library makes functions available that permit a standardized
interchange of data betweeen various applications. The following
routines are present for this purpose:

!begin_xlist [x scrp_write] !compressed
!item [(!bullet) scrp_clear]
Deletes files in the clipboard
!item [(!bullet) scrp_read]
Obtains path of the clipboard
!item [(!bullet) scrp_write]
Sets path of the clipboard
!end_xlist

(!B)Note:(!b) Besides these functions, some other particulars have to be
taken into account for
(!link [exchanging data via the clipboard][Data exchange via the GEM clipboard]).

See also: Messages ~ SC_CHANGED ~ SH_WDRAW ~ Style guidelines

